The Supplier shall supply dock shelters:

Type: {{shelterType}}, Quantity: {{shelterQty}}

Per unit:
- Clear opening: {{clearWidth}} × {{clearHeight}} mm
- Projection: {{projection}} mm
- Fabric: {{fabricMaterial}}
- Frame: {{frameType}}
- Colour: {{colour}}

Compatibility with the overhead door and dock leveller shall be confirmed by the Supplier prior to order.

The Supplier shall confirm in the quotation: type, clear opening, projection, fabric specification, weather resistance rating, fire class, expected service life.

STM reserves the right to reject non-compliant alternatives.

The Supplier shall supply per dock shelter the following accessories:

- Guide rails: {{guideRails}}
- Dock light: {{dockLight}}
- Signage: dock number plate, standard

All accessories shall be compatible with the supplied shelter type. The Supplier shall confirm compatibility and state any accessories not included in the base price.

STM reserves the right to reject non-compliant alternatives.
